Name: Circe Hooded Ice Fleece
Short description: This is a variable product called a Circe Hooded Ice Fleece
description:
Keep shivers at bay with the Circe Hooded Ice Fleece. Ultra-thick, high-pile fleece traps your body heat and keeps cold outside. The drawstring hood and ribbed details add extra coziness and touches of classic style. Its relaxed fit is loose enough to layer comfortably over your shirt.

Full-zip front.
Three-panel hood.
Flatlock seams throughout.
Welt hand pockets.
Machine wash/dry.

Short description: This is a simple product called Aim Analog Watch

Short description: This is a simple product called Endurance Watch
